  "title": "DESIGN COORDINATOR, ARCHITECTURE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Your Role</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work closely with a team of BIM Modellers in the design and coordination works</li>\n  <li>Responsible for preparing construction drawings including shop drawings submissions and approvals.</li>\n  <li>Supervise work progress on site, and liaise closely with consultants, sub-contractors and operation team</li>\n  <li>Involved in tendering work</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Architecture with minimum 3 years’ relevant experience with a main construction firm</li>\n  <li>Be able to read and understand construction drawings</li>\n  <li>Has project experience in buildings / hotels</li>\n  <li>Be meticulous, highly motivated and independent with excellent team spirit and interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>",
